replies.bodyText:
I wasn't particularly attracted to the output of:
"enabled": {
  "user": { "name" : "example" },
  "enabled": false
}

But I suppose, I can nest the enable/disable structure under the change name if you believe it is more consistent this way.

Ie. like this:
"change": {
  "disable": {
    "user": { "name": "example"}
  }
}
